item.title: Red Ring of Penis Death: Milla of One Condom’s Sex Stories
item.description: Milla was born to talk about sexual health–she spent her adolescence figuring out how and now her dreams are coming true as the Marketing & Communications director for ONE Condoms. She tells Wyoh about being the first person people talk openly with about sex, helping people overcome penis anxiety, condom fashion shows, her dreams for a new-age glory hole, and gets nerdy about condom manufacturing, sustainability, and the newest in condom technology... item.title: 211: The Drier, the Burnier
item.description: A cornucopia of great questions graced our podcasting table this month, and from it we drew such topics as (not) mixing and matching your RAM, fishing for game saves in AppData, an appreciation of the demoscene past and present, the redundant measurements that are totally the power company's fault, and the unmitigated decadence of the Tim Tam slam...
